data.description: Wait until you see this beauty by the beach! From the location just a stones throw away from America's first public beach to to the curb appeal - this three bedroom single family in the Point of Pines is a show stopper. Immaculately maintained by the same family for generations. Gleaming hardwood floors, a working fireplace, two bathrooms, a large fenced in yard and one detached covered entry car garage complete this dream. Oh, we almost forgot, an additional 3,000 sq ft fenced side lot (partially housing sunroom) is included. Easy access to the Blue Line and 1A makes commuting just minutes to Boston, Logan Airport and all major routes. Commuter Open House this Thursday from 5:30-7PM. Offers due noon 5/24 - Seller reserves the right to accept an offer prior to the deadline.
